        },
        "text": "Eurofinas, the voice of specialised consumer credit providers at the EU level, represents finance houses, specialised banks, captive finance companies of car, equipment, etc. manufacturers and universal banks. By enabling responsible access to credit for European consumers, our members promote social mobility, inclusion, and economic growth across Europe.",
