          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 3793,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "We therefore encourage the Commission to focus on the effective and consistent enforcement of the robust legislation already in place, rather than introducing parallel or overlapping requirements.",
