          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 3524,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Consumer credit providers already operate under one of the EU's most comprehensive and interlinked regulatory frameworks, which ensures consumer protection both online and offline. This includes:",
