          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 11414,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "The GDPR guarantees fairness, transparency, and accountability in data processing, including profiling and automated decision-making. It already regulates many of the digital practices, e.g. personalisation and targeting. Coupled with the AI Act, which introduces more precise requirements for high-risk AI systems, including those used for creditworthiness assessment, a comprehensive framework is already in place.",
