          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 4312,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Together, these instruments create a coherent and future-proof framework that comprehensively protects consumers engaging with credit providers in digital settings.",
        "chunk_meta": {
