          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "In this regard, Eurofinas strongly welcomes strengthened coordination between sectoral and horizontal regulatory stakeholders, i.e. financial supervisors, data protection authorities, and consumer protection authorities. Moreover, clear recognition of compliance with existing obligations under already applicable frameworks in addressing the goals sought through the DFA.",
